691
00:52:30.820 --> 00:52:31.950
Co to dě...

692
00:52:31.950 --> 00:52:33.320
Ma-Manažere Oh!

693
00:52:33.320 --> 00:52:34.910
Můj bože.

694
00:52:36.120 --> 00:52:38.750
